    <body>
        <ol>
            <li>key "abs" defines a term, surface form, and acronym.</li>
            <li>xref reference to abs, should be full term: <xref keyref="abs"/></li>
            <li>keyword reference to abs, should be full term: <keyword keyref="abs"/></li>
            <li>Term reference to abs, should be surface form: <term keyref="abs"></term></li>
            <li>First abbreviated form to abs, should be acronym: <abbreviated-form keyref="abs"/></li>
        </ol>
        
        <p>
            <ol>
                <li>key "a" reference to a topic</li>
                <li>xref reference to a:<xref keyref="a"></xref></li>
                <li>keyword reference to a:<keyword keyref="a"></keyword></li>
               <li>Term reference to a:<term keyref="a">TERM REF A</term></li>
            </ol> 
        </p>
        
       <ol>
           <li>conkeyref</li>
       </ol>
        <p conkeyref="a/p1"></p>
        <p conkeyref="a/p2"></p>
        
        <ol>
            <li>Define a keyword,which content is "KEYWORD"</li>
            <li>term pulls keyword: <term keyref="keyword"/></li>
            <li>keyword pulls keyword: <keyword keyref="keyword"/></li>
            <!--<li>xref pulls keyword: <xref keyref="keyword"/></li>  -->

        </ol>
        
        <ol>
            <li>ph tag could has the attribute "keyref"</li>
            <li>ph reference to a:<ph keyref="a"></ph></li>
            <li>ph reference to abs:<ph keyref="abs"></ph></li>
            <li>ph reference to keyword:<ph keyref="keyword"></ph></li>
        </ol>
        
        <ol>
            <li>dt tag could has the attribute "keyref"</li>
            <li>
                <dl>
                    <dlentry>
                        <dt keyref="a">keyref a</dt>
                        <dd>...........................</dd>
                    </dlentry>
                    <dlentry>
                        <dt keyref="abs">keyref abs</dt>
                        <dd>...........................</dd>
                    </dlentry>
                    <dlentry>
                        <dt keyref="keyword">keyref keyword</dt>
                        <dd>...........................</dd>
                    </dlentry>
                </dl>
            </li>
        </ol>
        
        <ol>
            <li>image tag could has the attribute "keyref"</li>
            <li><image href="image/1.gif" keyref="a"></image></li>
            <li><image href="image/2.gif" keyref="abs"></image></li>
            <li><image href="image/3.gif" keyref="keyword"></image></li>
        </ol>
        
        <ol>
            <li>cite tag could has the attribute "keyref"</li>
            <li>
                <p>The keyref a: <cite keyref="a"></cite></p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>The keyref abs: <cite keyref="abs"></cite></p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>The keyref keyword: <cite keyref="keyword"></cite></p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        
        <ol>
            <li>lq  tag could has the attribute "keyref"</li>
